{"tid":1566351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋佳節祝各位黑警死全家","createTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:00:07.000Z","uid":164590,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"40d4e5d27d5293bb7e8d0c7b6d781d2232cb21aa","tid":1566351,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"老婆做雞，個囡俾狗屌，個仔生癌死<br />\n自己長命百歲百病纏身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e0e6191dcd5ce22e084f321a73722d534d013e","tid":1566351,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aada5b22d26564ed596fe309a48a9baa6bcf3adf","tid":1566351,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34264e6edd84469159aae2f3f430860bba9e0e5e","tid":1566351,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7eb2716ad0bf82785a199bcd8bdb04bf2293d01","tid":1566351,"u